1. Policija je pokrenula *istragu* o nestalom automobilu. (The police initiated an *investigation* into the missing car.)
2. Advokat je insistirao na temeljitoj *istragi* kako bi se dokazala nevinost njegovog klijenta. (The lawyer insisted on a thorough *investigation* in order to prove his client's innocence.)
3. Mediji su objavili da je *istraga* o korupciji u vladi u tijeku. (The media reported that the *investigation* into government corruption was underway.)
4. *Istraga* je pokazala da je uzrok požara kvar na električnoj instalaciji. (The *investigation* revealed that the cause of the fire was a malfunction in the electrical system.)
5. Prijatelj mi je rekao da je *istraga* protiv mene započela i da ću biti optužen za pronevjeru novca. (My friend told me that an *investigation* against me had started and that I would be charged with embezzlement.)
6. Osumnjičeni je u pritvoru dok se *istraga* ne završi. (The suspect is in custody until the *investigation* is complete.)
7. *Istrage* su otkrile da je poznati biznismen bio uključen u pranje novca. (Investigations uncovered that a well-known businessman was involved in money laundering.)
8. Učitelj je obavijestio roditelje da će biti provedena *istraga* o navodnoj školskoj prevari. (The teacher informed the parents that an *investigation* would be conducted into the alleged school fraud.)
9. Državno tužilaštvo je naložilo pokretanje *istrage* protiv ministra zbog sumnje u zloupotrebu položaja. (The state prosecutor's office ordered an *investigation* to be launched against the minister for suspected abuse of power.)
10. *Istraga* je otkrila da je zaposlenik poduzeća pronevjerio više od milion dolara. (The *investigation* revealed that an employee of the company embezzled more than one million dollars.)